description: Newspaper with a focus on African-American issues
label: San Francisco Bay View
title: San_Francisco_Bay_View
exrest: The San Francisco Bay View National Black Newspaper is an online and print newspaper, published in San Francisco, California. It covers events from an African-American perspective, with a focus on Black liberation and coverage of worldwide racial inequality and political repression. The newspaper's distribution in its print edition extends to the larger San Francisco Bay Area and it is mailed to subscribers, including prisoners, across the United States. Its name refers to the Bayview-Hunters Point neighborhood.
